{"tid":1439213,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"我宣佈第四罷 - 罷網","createTime":"2019-08-10T04:38:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T10:03:30.000Z","uid":277533,"like":4,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"406f6be52b8fb53aee09f8513d9eefaaaf5acc38","tid":1439213,"uid":277533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T04:38:41.000Z","msg":"【蘋聞追Click】IT人研發AI認警察程式 竟涉教唆謀殺被捕可囚終身<br />\n [url]<a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190810&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=59911383/[url]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190810%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D59911383%2F%5Burl%5D&d=sJhP54gyZlpQHD%2BOhJ68s5R%2B4kUINcy65scadR%2F1ewI%3D&h=fa2ab89a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190810%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D59911383%2F%5Burl%5D&h=bba5b8d8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190810&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=59911383/[url]</a><br />\n<br />\nIT界嘅影響力應該好大，網民影響力仲大<br />\n<br />\n有無可能<br />\n<br />\n1. 將d app集體下架或更新反送中version，<br />\n<br />\n2. social media統一集體轉發一篇文章，twitter，facebook，IG同時做<br />\n<br />\n3. 將網店暫停一天，貼統一文章，幫手罷買<br />\n<br />\n4. 令最難統一嘅網民統一對付暴政，第五權可能就係網民，令最世界都沒辦法唔接收資訊<br />\n<br />\n我宣佈第四罷就係 - 罷網<br />\n<br />\n罷網唔係咩都唔做，而係統一網絡力量，令全世界知道，令唔想收到資訊既人都知道，我哋做緊咩野<br />\n<br />\n大家有咩意見？"},{"pid":"1949e8246eaf974a2dd3079ab9b3ab2fce82f9d2","tid":1439213,"uid":246371,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T04:39:31.000Z","msg":"你覺得有幾多人會聽你講？"},{"pid":"08564fb618bd9c01251a110b0c3097977c705f47","tid":1439213,"uid":277533,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T04:39:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190810&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=59911383\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190810%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D59911383&d=sJhP54gyZlpQHD%2BOhJ68s5R%2B4kUINcy65scadR%2F1